@startuml
title LeninKart Deployment Control Flow
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Segoe UI
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.4
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceParticipant { BackgroundColor white; BorderColor #475569 }
actor Operator
participant Jira
participant "GitHub Actions\nDeploy From Jira" as GHA
participant "Self-hosted Runner" as Runner
participant "deployment-poc" as POC
participant "leninkart-infra\nGitOps repo" as Infra
participant "ArgoCD\nin k3d cluster" as Argo
participant "Kubernetes Workloads" as K8s
participant "project-validation\nobserver only" as PV
Operator -> Jira : create / update request
Operator -> GHA : workflow_dispatch(jira_ticket)
GHA -> Runner : schedule job
Runner -> POC : execute
POC -> Jira : fetch metadata + progress
POC -> Infra : update values + push
Infra -> Argo : new desired revision
POC -> Argo : wait for sync + health\nverify exact GitOps revision
Argo -> K8s : reconcile workloads
POC -> Jira : final comment + transition
PV ..> GHA : CI proof
PV ..> Infra : GitOps proof
PV ..> Argo : sync / health proof
PV ..> K8s : UI proof
note right of GHA
Manual trigger model:\nJira ticket creation alone\ndoes not auto-dispatch.
end note
note right of K8s
Kafka remains outside this control flow\nas a Docker Compose runtime dependency.
end note
@enduml
